          "_name": "features10",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"features10\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Icons\" name=\"showIcons\" checked>\n        <select title=\"Cards\" name=\"cardsAmount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">3</option>\n            <option value=\"4\" selected>4</option>\n        </select>\n\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Background Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/3d-render-modern-background-with-plexus-design-2000x1500.webp\" parallax selected>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" value=\"#232323\">\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Background Video\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uNCr7NdOJgw\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#2e2e2e\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.6\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"card p-3 col-12 col-md-6\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-3': cardsAmount == '4',\n                             'col-lg-4': cardsAmount == '3'}\">\n                <div class=\"media mb-3\">\n                    <div class=\"card-img align-self-center\" mbr-if=\"showIcons\">\n                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbri-globe-2\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 80px;\"></span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h4 class=\"card-title media-body py-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-img\"><b>ACESSO ILIMITADO</b></h4>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card-box\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">Internet sempre, sem bloqueios, sem limite de dados, você poderá navegar tranquilamente na internet sem se preocupar com franquia de banda e sem redução de velocidade.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"card p-3 col-12 col-md-6\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 1\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-3': cardsAmount == '4',\n                             'col-lg-4': cardsAmount == '3'}\">\n                <div class=\"media mb-3\">\n                    <div class=\"card-img align-self-center\" mbr-if=\"showIcons\">\n                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbri-globe\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 80px;\"></span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h4 class=\"card-title media-body py-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-img\"><b>\n                        MAIOR COBERTURA</b></h4>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card-box\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">Na M2 oferecemos serviço de internet banda larga que chega aonde você precisa, conectando passeios, usinas e fazendas onde grande parte dos provedores de internet não estão disponíveis ou apresentam limitações.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"card p-3 col-12 col-md-6\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 2\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-3': cardsAmount == '4',\n                             'col-lg-4': cardsAmount == '3'}\">\n                <div class=\"media mb-3\">\n                    <div class=\"card-img align-self-center\" mbr-if=\"showIcons\">\n                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbri-wifi\" style=\"font-size: 80px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h4 class=\"card-title media-body py-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-img\"><b>\n                        DISPONIBILIDADE DE IPS VALIDOS</b></h4>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card-box\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">Para você poder ficar conectado a sua empresa a qualquer momento, oferecemos ips validos para acesso remoto ou monitoramento de cameras.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"card p-3 col-12 col-md-6\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount > 3\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-3': cardsAmount == '4',\n                             'col-lg-4': cardsAmount == '3'}\">\n                <div class=\"media mb-3\">\n                    <div class=\"card-img align-self-center\" mbr-if=\"showIcons\">\n                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbri-growing-chart\" style=\"font-size: 80px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h4 class=\"card-title media-body py-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-img\"><b>\n                        GARANTIA DE BANDA</b></h4>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card-box\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">A M2 conta com uma tecnologia robusta e de qualidade, para você estudar, assistir vídeos, ouvir música ou navegar de forma confiável, garantindo acesso mesmo em clima nublado ou chuvas intensas.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise4",
          "_cid": "uig66dowc1",
